        <accessrestrict id="ref16">
            <head>Access Restrictions</head>
            <p>Open for research without restrictions.</p>
        </accessrestrict>
        <scopecontent id="ref14">
            <head>Scope and Content Note</head>
            <p>The collection contains twelve oral history interviews taken by Kelley and one recorded radio program. The collection documents the experiences of individuals involved with the Alabama Communist Party during the Great Depression.</p>
        </scopecontent>
